    *   **Comprehensive MCP Update (MANDATORY FINAL STEP):** (Per [loop.mdcc](mdc:.cursor/rules/loop.mdcc) Step 6.4) `mcp_project-manager_update_task_tasks__task_id__put(task_id=self.taskId, title=self.original_title + " (Analysis & Proposals for PM)", description=self.original_description + "\\n---\\n" + detailed_analysis_summary_for_current_task, status=final_status_for_mcp, completed=True)`. This call concludes your turn. 🏁
